{"word":"H1120 - בָּמֹות - Bâmôwth - baw-moth' - Bamoth","slug":"H1120","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּמֹות</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Bâmôwth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>baw-moth'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bamoth"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05EA; &#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&#x05DC;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05EA; - ba&#x0302;mo&#x0302;th  ba&#x0302;mo&#x0302;th ba&#x201B;al</b> - <i>baw-moth', baw-moth' bah'-al</i><p/>Plural of <a href=\"#/H1116\">H1116</a>; <i>heights</i>; the second form is a more complete form of the first form; from the same and <a href=\"#/H1168\">H1168</a>; <i>heights of Baal</i>; <i>Bamoth</i> or <i>Bamoth Baal</i>, a place East of the Jordan: - Bamoth, Bamoth-baal."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1110\">H1110</a>, <a href=\"#/H1111\">H1111</a>, <a href=\"#/H1114\">H1114</a>, <a href=\"#/H1116\">H1116</a>, <a href=\"#/H1117\">H1117</a>, <a href=\"#/H1118\">H1118</a>"}]}